4. Reverse number 
“I extract the last digit using modulus, add it to the reversed number, and then remove the last digit using division. I repeat this until the number becomes zero.”
<!-- 
let num = 123;
let rev = 0;

while(num > 0){
  let rem = num % 10;
  rev = rev * 10 + rem;
  num = Math.floor(num / 10);
}
console.log(rev); -->

