8. Fibonacci Series
Logic:
Next number = previous two numbers ka sum.
<!-- 
let n = 5;
let a = 0, b = 1;

for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {
  console.log(a);
  let next = a + b;
  a = b;
  b = next;
} -->


